    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I see in the [grammar for a source unit](https://docs.soliditylang.org/en/latest/grammar.html#a4.Solidity.sourceUnit) that the version value consists of separate tokens which means that they could be whitespace-separated and/or span multiple lines. So this is currently perfectly valid:\r\n```solidity\r\npragma solidity^\r\n\r\n\r\n0. 7.\r\n4\r\n\r\n;\r\n```",
